snippet.title: Crypt of the NecroDancer cinematic trailer
snippet.description:
Now available for Pre-Order at http://necrodancer.com
Steam keys for PC and Mac will be provided at launch.

Music: Danny Baranowsky http://dannybmusic.com/
Trailer: Marlon Wiebe http://mr.mwiebe.com
Art: Ted Martens http://www.tedmartens.com/ and Jesse Turner https://twitter.com/jouste
Audio: Kevin Regamey http://powerupaudio.com/

Follow our progress on Twitter and Facebook:
http://twitter.com/necrodancergame
http://facebook.com/CryptOfTheNecroDancer

Or visit our forums where we're developing the game in public: http://braceyourselfgames.com/forums
